Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.00,0:00:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,（科米）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.17,0:00:50.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rMerged}-[chair creaks] -Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.51,0:00:56.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rMerged}[breathes heavily] Mmm. Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.72,0:00:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,什么事？\N{\rMerged}-Oh. -What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.81,0:00:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,-罗夫？ -什么事？\N{\rMerged}-Rowlf? -What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.89,0:01:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你这段时间都在弹琴吗？\N{\rMerged}Have you been playing this whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.19,0:01:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你以为是什么？\N{\rMerged}Well, what did you think it was?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.36,0:01:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你脑海中的怀旧集锦吗？\N{\rMerged}Some kinda sentimental montage in your head?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.65,0:01:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我们又要表演了，青蛙\N{\rMerged}-[mutters] -We're doing the show again, frog.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.53,0:01:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,对哦\N{\rMerged}[gasps] Oh, that's right. Uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.61,0:01:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,斯库特，时候到了\N{\rMerged}Scooter, it's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.45,0:01:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题，老大\N{\rMerged}You got it, boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.33,0:01:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,莎宾娜卡本特，30秒后开演，卡本特小姐\N{\rMerged}Sabrina Carpenter. Thirty seconds to curtain, Ms. Carpenter.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.91,0:01:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,卡本特小姐？\N{\rMerged}Ms. Carpenter?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.25,0:01:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你，斯库特\N{\rMerged}Thank you, Scooter.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.83,0:01:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊，是你，我好爱你的衣服\N{\rMerged}Oh, my God. It's you. I love your outfit. [chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.84,0:01:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是，你得换衣服\N{\rMerged}So do I. You're gonna have to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.38,0:01:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,是，女士\N{\rMerged}Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.76,0:01:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我的假发吗？\N{\rMerged}Is that my wig?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.05,0:01:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我不戴假发的，这是我的真发\N{\rMerged}I don't wear wigs. This is my real hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.35,0:01:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我也一样\N{\rMerged}Oh. Yeah. Same.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.97,0:01:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,-不，我…我知道 -不，我知道你知道\N{\rMerged}-No, I… And I know that. -No, I know you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.77,0:01:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,-很好 -好\N{\rMerged}-Great. -Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.14,0:01:41.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rMerged}[trumpet blares]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.94,0:01:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,《大青蛙布偶秀：特别场》
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.15,0:01:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎观赏《大青蛙布偶秀：特别场》 特别嘉宾是莎宾娜卡本特\N{\rMerged}It's The Muppet Show with our very special guest star, Sabrina Carpenter. [cheers]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.77,0:01:49.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rMerged}[audience cheers]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.86,0:01:55.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rMerged}[♪ "The Muppet Show Theme Song" playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.00,0:02:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,该演奏音乐，该点亮灯光\N{\rMerged}♪ It's time to play the music It's time to light the lights ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.17,0:02:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,该见见今晚登场的布偶了\N{\rMerged}♪ It's time to meet the Muppets On The Muppet Show tonight ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.34,0:02:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,该化好妆容，该好好打扮\N{\rMerged}♪ It's time to put on makeup It's time to dress up right ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.51,0:02:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,该揭开今晚《大青蛙布偶秀》的序幕了\N{\rMerged}♪ It's time to raise the curtain On The Muppet Show tonight ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.26,0:02:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我们干嘛老是来这里？\N{\rMerged}♪ Why do we always come here? ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.35,0:02:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,这个问题大概永远无解\N{\rMerged}♪ I guess we'll never know ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.43,0:02:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,被迫看这场秀\N{\rMerged}♪ It's like a kind of torture ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.52,0:02:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,有点像酷刑\N{\rMerged}♪To have to watch the show ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.06,0:02:32.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rMerged}[music continues]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.19,0:02:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,但现在让我们开演吧\N{\rMerged}♪ But now let's get things started ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.28,0:02:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你们快开演吧\N{\rMerged}♪ Why don't you get things started? ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.32,0:02:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,该开演了\N{\rMerged}♪ It's time to get things started ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.24,0:02:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,最令人惊叹、鼓舞人心 欢欣喜悦、布偶天成\N{\rMerged}♪ On the most sensational, inspirational Celebrational, Muppetational ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.50,0:02:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我们的《大青蛙布偶秀》\N{\rMerged}♪ This is what we call The Muppet Show ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.25,0:02:50.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rMerged}[trumpet screeches]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.75,0:02:52.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rMerged}[audience laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.58,0:02:53.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rMerged}[screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.84,0:02:56.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rMerged}[audience cheering]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.39,0:02:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢…谢谢\N{\rMerged}Thank you. Thank you. [mutters] Uh, thank you. [chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.47,0:03:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,大家好，欢迎观赏《大青蛙布偶秀》\N{\rMerged}Hi-ho, and welcome to The Muppet Show, everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.01,0:03:04.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rMerged}[audience cheering]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.52,0:03:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我们很高兴能回到这个舞台 一切就是从这里开始\N{\rMerged}You know, we are so excited to be back on the very stage where it all started,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.23,0:03:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,然后结束，然后\N{\rMerged}and then ended, and then,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.94,0:03:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,可能会再次开始，看今晚表现如何啰\N{\rMerged}is maybe starting again depending on how tonight goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.70,0:03:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,他们居然要重演老戏码\N{\rMerged}Hmph. I can't believe they're doing the old show again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.16,0:03:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好好的何必改\N{\rMerged}Well, if it ain't broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.49,0:03:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不，他们是好穷，所以才会来表演\N{\rMerged}No, they are broke. That's why they're doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.41,0:03:23.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rMerged}-[laughs] -[audience laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.41,0:03:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好，为我们开场的是\N{\rMerged}Okay. Now to kick us off,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.12,0:03:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的特别来宾\N{\rMerged}it's our very special guest,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.79,0:03:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,轰动乐坛的创作歌手，世界级的巨星\N{\rMerged}a sensational singer-songwriter and global superstar,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.38,0:03:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,独一无二的莎宾娜卡本特\N{\rMerged}-the one and only, Sabrina Carpenter. Yay! -[audience cheers]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.29,0:03:37.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rMerged}[laughing, clamoring]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.05,0:03:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,安静点，一群混混\N{\rMerged}Ugh. Quiet. [groans] Hooligans.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.01,0:03:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,快点，丢他\N{\rMerged}Do it. Do it. Toss. [laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.22,0:03:43.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rMerged}[yelps, grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.89,0:03:46.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rMerged}[laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.14,0:03:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,住手，否则赶你们出去\N{\rMerged}Stop, or you'll be removed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.44,0:03:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,别担心，山姆，交给我\N{\rMerged}Don't worry, Sam. I got it.
