Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.06,0:03:56.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rMerged}[laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.66,0:04:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你说手机坏了，其实是忘了充电\N{\rMerged}♪ You said your phone was broken Just forgot to charge it ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.91,0:04:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你这身行头，天啊，希望你是在搞笑\N{\rMerged}♪ Whole outfit you're wearing God, I hope it's ironic ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.71,0:04:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚说你完事了？ 我都不知道我们开始了\N{\rMerged}♪ Did you just say you're finished? Didn't know we started ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.50,0:04:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这一切都太熟悉了，宝贝，是什么来着？\N{\rMerged}♪ It's all just so familiar, baby What do you call it? ♪
