Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.23,0:06:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,真厉害\N{\rMerged}-Great talent! -Whoo-hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.78,0:06:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-我喜欢，再来 -对，太棒了\N{\rMerged}-Love it! More! More! -[chuckles] Yes, it's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.28,0:06:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好令人兴奋的开场，科米叔叔\N{\rMerged}Wow, what an exciting opening, Uncle Kermit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.24,0:06:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,做得好，鸡群，风扇的事真的很抱歉\N{\rMerged}Great job, Chickens. Again, I'm sorry about the fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.74,0:06:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我好羞愧\N{\rMerged}-[grunting] -[Sam] I'm mortified.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.04,0:06:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,-斯库特，过来 -好\N{\rMerged}-Scooter. Come here, come here, come here. -Uh. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.71,0:06:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,后台怎么这么拥挤？\N{\rMerged}Why is it so crowded back here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.29,0:06:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这些都是表演名单上的人，老大\N{\rMerged}Well, uh, these are all the acts in the show, boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.79,0:06:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定我批准那名单了吗？\N{\rMerged}What? Are you sure I approved all of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.46,0:06:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,还有更多呢\N{\rMerged}And more.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.54,0:06:22.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rMerged}[whistle blows]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.34,0:06:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我们快走，该上台了\N{\rMerged}[Muppet 1] Let's go already. We gotta get on stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.68,0:06:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,记得大家多期待参与我们首场回归秀吗？\N{\rMerged}Remember how excited everyone was to be on our first show back?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.89,0:06:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你还一直跟他们说 他们的表演听起来很有趣\N{\rMerged}And you kept telling them that their acts sounded fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.43,0:06:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,斯库特，大家都知道“听起来很有趣”\N{\rMerged}[scoffs] Scooter, everybody knows that "that sounds fun"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.02,0:06:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是一种委婉拒绝的方式\N{\rMerged}is just a polite way of saying no.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.31,0:06:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,对，还蛮隐晦的，老大\N{\rMerged}Yeah, that feels pretty indirect, boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.15,0:06:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,这可能会造成问题\N{\rMerged}-Hmm. -You know, this could be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.07,0:06:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好，下一个找我谈的人一定会被删掉\N{\rMerged}Okay. Well, the next person who talks to me is definitely getting cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.49,0:06:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,科米\N{\rMerged}-Mm-hmm. -Oh, Kermie.
